		<item name="wcf.help.item.tagging.description"><![CDATA[<p class="helpImage border container-4"><img src="{@RELATIVE_WCF_DIR}images/help/helpTagging1.png" alt="" /><span class="smallFont light">Tag cloud</span></p>
<p>Tags are words that describe and/or categorize elements such as images or a posts. Think of it as a kind of a summary of the content. The advantage is that you can search by <a href="index.php?page=TaggedObjects{@SID_ARG_2ND}">tags</a>, so you don't have to think hard about good search terms. You can easily find all photos with a sun on them if they are tagged with &quot;sun&quot;. So called tag clouds display tags in different sizes, accordig to the quantity of being used, thus tags used more often are displayed larger.</p>]]></item>
